<h3 id="start-coding"><a class="header-anchor" href="#start-coding" aria-hidden="true">¶</a> Start coding</h3>
<p>Now you have implemented Vue and Element to your project, and it's time to write your code. Start development mode:</p>
<pre><code class="hljs language-bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># visit localhost:8086</span>
npm run dev
</code></pre>
<p>Build:</p>
<pre><code class="hljs language-bash">npm run build
</code></pre>
<p>Please refer to each component's documentation to learn how to use them.</p>
</section></template>

